Directory Structure:

PanduAI_task/
├── Assets/
│   ├── green_image.mp4
│   ├── image.png
│   ├── image1.png
│   ├── video.mp4
│   └── white-background.jpg
├── background_remover/
│   ├── background_remover.py
└── image_video_mover/
    ├── left_to_write_movement.py
    └── zig-zag-movement.py


// Initialize the .mp4 and .png files in the Assets folder(in the same name format) before running the code 

python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

// For left to right movement
python3 image_video_mover/left_to_write_movement.py

// For zig-zag movement
python3 image_video_mover/zig-zag-movement.py

// For background remover
python3 background_remover/background_remover.py
